{"id":355828,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":16}],"page":"3","source":"“诗刊”","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"101","ytitle":"","mtitle":"闻长江大桥成喜赋","ftitle":"","authors":["董必武"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"董必武"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天堑分南北，三城鼎足然。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦思仙杖化，喜见铁虹悬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武汉连一气，龟蛇在两端。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔流不尽，荡荡路无偏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄鹤楼非旧，晴川阁尚全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游观当日暮，何物惹愁牵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年六月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(原载“诗刊”)"}]}